TO COMPILE:

	- In base directory 		--->		"make clear" and then "make all"

TO EXECUTE CLIENT:

	- In "client" directory 	--->		"sudo ./palma-client -c ../configs/[client config xml file]"

TO EXECUTE SERVER:

	- In "server" directory 	--->		"sudo ./palma-server -c ../configs/[server config xml file]"

TO EXECUTE TESTS:

	-In "test" directory		--->		"sudo ./[test-filename].py"
